# Django AWS CI/CD Deployment

## Architecture
GitHub -> Aws Codepipeline -> AWS CodeDeploy -> EC2 -> Django App

## Features
- Automated deployment using CodeDeploy
- Bash scripts for lifecycle hooks
- CI/CD integration

## Setup Steps
1. Launch EC2
2. Install CodeDeploy agent
3. Connect GitHub
4. Deploy application

## Tech Stack
- AWS EC2
- CodeDeploy
- codepipeline
- Django
- Bash
